c: 4
v: 43
t: "Ko onon yo gim…óim…ìe, wata on …ìa…óto julde den hara ko on siwru…ìe haa anndon ko wowloton ; wanaa ka moddu…óon e lonngal, si wanaa hara ko on ta∆¥itoo…ìe laawol haa la…ì…ìino…óon. Si on laatike nawnu…ìe, maa hi…óon e hoore jahal, maa …ìaawo hoggo arii go…ó…óo e mon(yaadon dow wuro), maa on soccondirii e rew…ìe …ìen on he…ìaali ndiyam, taamoree mbullaari(leydi) laa…ìundi : mowlon geece mon …óen e juu…óe mon …óen. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo Yawtanoowo"